title: Slug on Leaf
description: An illustration of a brown slug resting on a green leaf. The slug has a smooth, elongated body with a shiny surface, and its tentacles are extended.

title: Shrimp Illustration
description: An illustration of a shrimp, showcasing its elongated body, antennae, and segmented abdomen. The shrimp is depicted in shades of orange and green, with fine details highlighting its features.

title: Grasshopper
description: A detailed illustration of a grasshopper, showcasing its vibrant colors and distinct features such as long antennae and powerful hind legs.

title: Squid
description: An illustration of a squid, showcasing its elongated body, large eyes, and multiple tentacles.

title: Blue Dragonfly
description: A detailed illustration of a blue dragonfly with transparent wings. The dragonfly is depicted from a top-down view, showcasing its elongated body and delicate wing structure.

title: Mussel Shell
description: A close-up image of a mussel shell, showcasing its elongated, oval shape and iridescent dark blue and brown colors. The shell has a smooth surface with subtle lines and a shiny appearance.

title: Grasshopper
description: A close-up image of a green grasshopper, showcasing its long antennae, large hind legs, and detailed body structure. The background is white, emphasizing the grasshopper's vibrant green coloration and intricate patterns.

title: Sea Urchin
description: A colorful sea urchin with long, spiky red and purple spines protruding from a round, grayish base.

title: Ladybug
description: An illustration of a ladybug, characterized by its bright red body with black spots and black legs. The ladybug is depicted from a top-down view, showcasing its rounded shape and distinct coloration.

title: Mosquito
description: A close-up image of a mosquito, showcasing its elongated body, long legs, and two pairs of wings. The mosquito is depicted in a detailed manner, highlighting its features against a white background.

title: Butterfly
description: A detailed illustration of a butterfly with translucent wings. The wings are predominantly white with thin, dark brown outlines, showcasing a delicate and intricate pattern. The body of the butterfly is dark, contrasting with the light wings.

title: Isopod
description: An illustration of an isopod, a type of crustacean characterized by its segmented body and multiple legs. The isopod has a dark brown, segmented exoskeleton and is depicted with antennae and a small, rounded body.
